### Sign up success
POST {{host}}/api/users/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "alice",
  "nickname": "Alice",
  "password": "password123!"
}

### Create user
POST {{host}}/api/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "username": "bob",
  "nickname": "Bob",
  "password": "password123!"
}

### Sign up duplicate username
POST {{host}}/api/users/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "alice",
  "nickname": "Alice Two",
  "password": "password123!"
}

### Sign up validation failure
POST {{host}}/api/users/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "",
  "nickname": "NoUsername",
  "password": "password123!"
}
